forwardRef in typescript

Syntax:

👉️ const CompName = forwardRef<RefType, PropType>((props,ref)=>{return < ref={ref}></>})
   export default CompName;
 
 	OR
 
👉️ const CompName: ForwardRefRenderFunction<RefType, PropType> = (props,ref)=>{return < ref={ref}></>}
   export default forwardRef(CompName);
 
 e.g: !Unsplash > ImageDetailModal.tsx
 
